  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457800704/hEC42F33C\" id=\"_r_a_10457800704\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10457800704\" title=\"\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eDon\u0026#39;t mess with pickles!\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457785600/h5D1597CE/consulting-workers-some-employees-parents-and-grandparents-had-worked-there-and-apparently-felt-so\" id=\"_r_a_10457785600\" width=\"782\" height=\"1030\" alt=\"P... I used to work at a pickle factory in Michigan. When the new owners took over they insisted they change the recipe that had been the same for over 50 years without consulting the workers. Some of the employees parents and grandparents had worked there and apparently felt so\" title=\"Don\u0026#39;t mess with pickles!\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457786112/h61B8D43D/quit-and-actually-enjoyed-both-recipes-but-now-cant-tolerate-smell-or-taste-pickles-used-love-them\" id=\"_r_a_10457786112\" width=\"780\" height=\"1210\" alt=\"strongly about the recipe that 13 people quit and the majority else were outside with signs the next days until eventually they switched it [almost] all the way back. None of those who quit came back. Edit: I didnt quit, and actually enjoyed both recipes. But, now I cant tolerate the smell or taste of pickles. I used to love them. :\\\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eThis story is incredible\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457785088/hD438E10F/teeth-spin-insanely-fast-well-my-crew-had-laid-down-dirt-limerock-and-clay-and-now-had-run-mixer\" id=\"_r_a_10457785088\" width=\"784\" height=\"1172\" alt=\"b... In the early 90s I worked for a large construction company in Florida. I was on the road crew. One of the machines we used was called a mixer. The objective of this machine was to mix up the subgrade of a road. It has giant teeth that spin insanely fast. Well my crew had laid down the dirt, limerock and clay and now had to run the mixer\" title=\"This story is incredible\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457785856/h481E52E2/this-cable-down-luckily-wasnt-at-work-day-came-next-day-anyone-who-even-near-incident-got-fired\" id=\"_r_a_10457785856\" width=\"794\" height=\"1052\" alt=\"over it. Well someone set the blades too low and ripped an international fiber optic cable out of the ground. A clean cut would have been bad but this cable was shredded beyond belief. It cost $100,000 per hour that this cable was down. Luckily I wasn\u0026#39;t at work that day. When I came in the next day anyone who was even near the incident got fired.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457785344/h6E5175D4/fused-back-together-cost-company-millions-total-about-40-people-were-fired-and-put-on-another-crew\" id=\"_r_a_10457785344\" width=\"788\" height=\"906\" alt=\"My whole crew was extinct. To put into perspective, the cable was fatter than your upper leg and composed of thousands of glass strands. Every strand had to be fused back together. It cost the company millions. Total about 40 people were fired and I was put on another crew.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457784832/h8DF27B2D/sub-grade-before-asphalt-goes-way-deeper-and-combines-different-layers-clay-limerock-and-dirt\" id=\"_r_a_10457784832\" width=\"792\" height=\"1160\" alt=\"Edit: Alot of you are messaging me confusing a mill it machine with a mixer. A Mill it machine only removes a layer of asphalt from the road for repaving. A road construction mixer is like a giant garden tiller that mixes up the different materials for the sub grade before the asphalt. It goes way deeper and combines different layers of clay, limerock and dirt.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eSometimes a massive mistake can happen in seconds, and there\u0026#39;s no easy way to fix it. In this case, the company lost millions in a matter of seconds, and the workers were very much fired, not quitters. It just goes to show how fragile one\u0026#39;s career really is! \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eYou love to see it\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457784576/hF544B416/at-over-4000-per-engineer-10-walked-and-rest-threatened-strike-boss-had-give-and-buy-tools-himself\" id=\"_r_a_10457784576\" width=\"786\" height=\"1094\" alt=\"Woojie All the engineers at one job I was in had their contracts changed to that they had to buy their own tools, Due to the specialist nature of our jobs we were all looking at over £4000 per engineer. 10 walked and the rest threatened to strike. The boss had to give in and buy the tools himself.\" title=\"You love to see it\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457786368/h0C3BD476/employees-can-be-fired-without-cause-and-asked-them-submit-resumes-if-they-wanted-their-jobs-back\" id=\"_r_a_10457786368\" width=\"782\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"FalstaffsMind I work in local Government for an urban county. One of the IT Departments, reclassified all their employees as Exempt (a designation designed for political appointments), fired them all (only Exempt employees can be fired without cause), and asked them to submit resumes if they wanted their jobs back.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457786624/h29E1A3C9/pull-stunt-like-word-gets-out-and-resumes-dont-come-flooding-they-are-still-trying-recover\" id=\"_r_a_10457786624\" width=\"760\" height=\"1222\" alt=\"Their goal was to get rid of some employees they felt were de d weight. But it turns out, the most valued employees, the ones with readily marketable skills in the prime of their careers, just shook their heads and had jobs elsewhere by the end of the week. Furthermore, when you pull a stunt like that, word gets out, and resumes don\u0026#39;t come flooding in. They are still trying to recover.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457786880/h82CCE2E3/went-bar-manager-collect-receipts-and-checkouts-plus-paychecks-few-weeks-examine-them-someone-is\" id=\"_r_a_10457786880\" width=\"742\" height=\"1182\" alt=\"[deleted] Worked in a bar in a nightclub. Restaurant by day, club by night. 5 bartenders behind the bar on any given Friday and Saturday, plus barbacks. Thought something was weird about our credit card tips - went to bar manager. We collect receipts and checkouts plus paychecks for a few weeks, examine them. Someone is\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457787136/hC96451CB/withheld-tips-bar-manager-signals-come-over-threatens-quit-if-owner-doesnt-return-money-he-stole\" id=\"_r_a_10457787136\" width=\"798\" height=\"1186\" alt=\"withholding quite a bit of our tips. Fast forward to a Friday night, busy as f Owner comes in to see how things. are going, bar manager confronts him. Owner denies wrongdoing, claims what he\u0026#39;s doing is legal (it wasn\u0026#39;t, he was pocketing the withheld tips). Bar manager signals for me to come over, threatens to quit if the owner doesn\u0026#39;t return the money he stole.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457787904/hC8C3045A/down-road-another-bar-commiserate-over-bulls-left-over-500-people-club-with-no-bar-staff-zero-f-s\" id=\"_r_a_10457787904\" width=\"788\" height=\"1128\" alt=\"Owner more or less says \u0026#34;tough sh \u0026#34;bar manager walks out. I lean into the bar long enough to tell one of the other bartenders what happened, give the owner a snarky wave, and follow him out. 5 minutes later, the rest of the bar staff joins us, and we wander down the road to another bar to commiserate over the bulls . Left over 500 people in the club with no bar staff. Zero f S\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457787392/h07A5EF58/and-quit-too-last-heard-they-had-shut-down-few-weeks-restaff-still-overly-proud-myself-f-guy\" id=\"_r_a_10457787392\" width=\"774\" height=\"808\" alt=\"given. Found out a few days later that the daytime serving staff heard what happened and quit too. Last I heard, they had to shut down for a few weeks to restaff. Still overly proud of myself for that. F that guy.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457791744/h4818A97F/ran-interviews-and-hired-woman-be-her-superior-they-never-asked-my-mom-apply-position-and-never\" id=\"_r_a_10457791744\" width=\"790\" height=\"1192\" alt=\"Oliverrr36 My mom used to work for a college. She started there as a secretary when the college was just starting out and gradually moved up until she was running the whole business department. Without her knowing, the college ran interviews and hired a woman to be her superior. They never asked my mom to apply for the position and never\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457790976/hBA1CF83C/so-she-sucked-up-and-trained-this-woman-while-putting-on-her-best-face-and-being-cordial-all-rest\" id=\"_r_a_10457790976\" width=\"794\" height=\"1194\" alt=\"mentioned it to her until the day this woman is introduced to her, and my mom\u0026#39;s boss informed my mom she was supposed to train this woman to be her boss for the department. My mom was clearly hurt and upset, but she needed her job and just couldn\u0026#39;t quit, so she sucked it up and trained this woman while putting on her best face and being cordial. All the rest of\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457790464/h58C0C4A4/mom-walks-through-doors-and-boss-college-is-waiting-her-he-brings-her-into-his-office-and-fires-her\" id=\"_r_a_10457790464\" width=\"756\" height=\"1032\" alt=\"the people who worked under my mom in the department could not stand this woman and were incredibly upset by the situation, as well. One morning, my mom walks through the doors, and the boss of the college is waiting for her. He brings her into his office and fires her.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457800960/hDBCD94AD/replace-my-mom-quit-and-they-had-b-call-my-mom-and-ask-her-back-can-guess-where-she-told-them-shove\" id=\"_r_a_10457800960\" width=\"786\" height=\"1128\" alt=\"Within the month, the rest of the department all quit, as well, leaving them to hire and train all new people right before fall semester started. Six months later, the woman they hired to replace my mom quit, and they had the b to call my mom and ask her back. You can guess where she told them to shove it.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e19\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457791232/h21646294/month-6-8-month-refusal-allow-people-go-part-time-have-lost-and-will-lose-15-20-people-by-end-month\" id=\"_r_a_10457791232\" width=\"786\" height=\"962\" alt=\"Heros tinc Several things are happening right now. Mandated 36 hour shifts. Mandated over time shifts changed from 2 a month to 6-8 a month. Refusal to allow people to go part time. We have lost and will lose 15-20 people by the end of the month.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u0