MBA). The son decided to relocate headquarters 500 miles away, close to his daddy\u0026#39;s headquarters. He gave us 30-days notice to\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e23\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457793024/hE61326F6/after-announcement-and-gave-two-weeks-notice-my-boss-went-ballistic-said-are-supported-do-no-one\" id=\"_r_a_10457793024\" width=\"788\" height=\"1182\" alt=\"move with no moving compensation or lose our jobs. Out of 300 employees, one moved. I had already been looking for a job, the writing was on the wall. I accepted a new position the day after the announcement and gave two weeks notice. My boss went ballistic, said \u0026#39;what are we supported to do!? No one\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e24\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457793280/h52C95153/out-business-within-60-days-after-move-four-months-after-acquisition-they-had-spent-50-million-buy\" id=\"_r_a_10457793280\" width=\"792\" height=\"892\" alt=\"can fill you job here and we won\u0026#39;t have anyone new until we move. You\u0026#39;re not a team player!\u0026#39; Bonus: The company was out of business within 60 days after the move, four months after the acquisition. They had spent $50 million to buy it.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457799168/hD38C9E75\" id=\"_r_a_10457799168\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10457799168\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e26\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457792512/hA4793AF0/our-company-instead-fired-600-people-one-day-one-them-hear-those-who-remained-place-is-awful-now\" id=\"_r_a_10457792512\" width=\"786\" height=\"1122\" alt=\"ShutUpHeExplai... Competing company in a similar but not identical line of business tried for years to replicate our product with no success. They scrapped. the project and took the R\u0026amp;D money and bought our company instead. Fired 600+ people in one day. I was one of them. I hear from those who remained the place is awful now.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e27\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457793536/h78BDA789/life-and-he-completely-dedicated-absentee-owners-had-hired-do-nothing-know-nothing-manager-after\" id=\"_r_a_10457793536\" width=\"790\" height=\"1186\" alt=\"awelldressedman I was the lead cook in a million dollar kitchen at a multi-million dollar high end restaurant. The executive chef had been there since they opened and worked his way from the bottom to the top in 4 years. That place was his whole life and he was completely dedicated to it. The absentee owners had hired a \u0026#34;do nothing, know nothing\u0026#34; manager. After\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e28\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457795072/h4666085C/rounds-golf-later-chef-comes-back-work-pink-slip-2730-employees-came-and-resigned-immediately-after\" id=\"_r_a_10457795072\" width=\"776\" height=\"1130\" alt=\"weeks of complaining, the owners had a meeting with the manager and gave him a week to get on top of his job. The chef went on vacation that week, the manager saw that as an opportunity to buddy up with owners. A week and 2 rounds of golf later the chef comes back to work to a pink slip. 27/30 employees came in and resigned immediately after.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e29\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457794048/h719BF25C/preferences-and-allocated-shifts-and-rotas-entirely-based-on-companys-needs-completely-invalidating\" id=\"_r_a_10457794048\" width=\"794\" height=\"1192\" alt=\"[deleted] My old workplace decided to do a complete overhaul of everyone\u0026#39;s rotas. They went through an entire consultation period, asking. people what they could and couldn\u0026#39;t work, then completely ignored everyone\u0026#39;s preferences and allocated shifts and rotas entirely based on the company\u0026#39;s needs, completely invalidating the\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457793792/h73DEA0F3/work-more-unsociable-hours-and-weekends-and-nobody-pleased-by-these-changes-lot-people-left\" id=\"_r_a_10457793792\" width=\"780\" height=\"574\" alt=\"entire consultation period. People were being asked/expected to work more unsociable hours and weekends, and nobody was pleased by these changes. A lot of people left.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e31\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457801472/hAAFE9808\" id=\"_r_a_10457801472\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10457801472\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e32\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457794304/h39955AEA/would-run-up-200-checks-which-fine-since-they-had-an-automatic-18-gratuity-being-such-large-party\" id=\"_r_a_10457794304\" width=\"768\" height=\"856\" alt=\"flamingopinknut... I worked at a Dave and busters in a fairly low income area. We had parties of 8 or more come in regularly, and they would run up $200 checks which was fine since they had an automatic 18% gratuity for being such a large party.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e33\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457794816/hAD98DC04/getting-regularly-stiffed-on-these-massive-checks-within-three-weeks-over-third-our-staff-quit\" id=\"_r_a_10457794816\" width=\"770\" height=\"742\" alt=\"They decided to eliminate the large party gratuity option in hopes that it would inspire servers to work harder. Instead we all started getting regularly stiffed on these massive checks. Within three weeks over a third of our staff quit.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e34\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457794560/h2846971B/mainly-known-take-out-or-delivery-only-store-located-shopping-center-with-several-other-businesses\" id=\"_r_a_10457794560\" width=\"756\" height=\"1082\" alt=\"PatrickRsGhost From what I understood, I caused a domino effect at a local big-chain pizza place. The pizza place I worked at wasn\u0026#39;t a full-service restaurant, which they\u0026#39;re mainly known for; it was a take-out or delivery only store, located in a shopping center with several other businesses.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e35\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457795584/hD2650910/he-preferred-be-driver-than-manager-third-manager-an-all-out-b-she-mistreated-employees-especially\" id=\"_r_a_10457795584\" width=\"786\" height=\"1208\" alt=\"During the two years I worked there, we had gone through three store managers. The first manager was awesome. He was firm, strict, but fair. The second manager was a bit of a ditz. He went by the book, but you could tell his heart wasn\u0026#39;t really in it. I think he preferred to be a driver than a manager. The third manager was an all-out b. She mistreated the employees, especially the\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e36\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457795328/hB5E3B75F/with-respect-she-basically-fired-she-said-resigned-didnt-care-no-longer-under-her-tyrannical-rule\" id=\"_r_a_10457795328\" width=\"780\" height=\"1126\" alt=\"men, and she\u0026#39;d do things. that only benefited her, not others. I was getting fed up. She had put a suggestion box outside her office. I wrote a very lengthy suggestion that she treat her employees with respect. She basically fired me. She said I\u0026#39;d resigned. I didn\u0026#39;t care. I was no longer under her tyrannical rule.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e37\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457796096/h95EC91C3/my-parents-ordered-pizza-pizza-places-major-competitor-they-asked-give-driver-money-and-did\" id=\"_r_a_10457796096\" width=\"788\" height=\"1202\" alt=\"A friend of mine who still worked there called me a week later and told me three other people quit because like me, they got tired of her sh.. Later that same year (I quit late Summer), about two weeks after Halloween, my parents ordered a pizza from that pizza place\u0026#39;s major competitor. They asked me to give the driver the money, and when I did, it\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e38\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457795840/h2D2B1B0C/rush-take-her-own-8-year-old-daughter-trick-or-treating-driver-now-working-competitor-told-she\" id=\"_r_a_10457795840\" width=\"796\" height=\"1132\" alt=\"turned out to be a driver I knew from the other place. She told me she quit on Halloween night because she wanted to take her 4- year-old trick-or-treating, but the manager said no, then she (the manager) took off early, in the middle of a rush, to take her own 8-year-old daughter trick-or-treating. The driver that was now working for the competitor told me she\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e39\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457796352/h784B5E19/and-manager-no-longer-there-she-and-her-husband-were-fired-due-stealing-money-store-karma-works\" id=\"_r_a_10457796352\" width=\"756\" height=\"1180\" alt=\"threw her hat at the manager, told her to f off, and quit right there. A year or two later, I ran into the old assistant manager, who was now working at an Arby\u0026#39;s. She told me many others had quit, and that manager was no longer there; she and her husband were fired, due to stealing money from that store. Karma...it works,\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e40\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10457806336/hDC2B6517/1-guy-left-an-office-where-there-are-5-people-working-is-15-company-leaving-thats-best-have\" id=\"_r_a_10457806336\" width=\"754\" height=\"694\" alt=\"PM_YOUR_FEELI... 1 guy left In an office where there are 5 people working that is 1/5 of the company leaving. thats the best I have ·- i\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003eStay up to date by following us on \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FailBlog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003